\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 y 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

 son las matrices respectivas de 
\begin_inset Formula $\langle\cdot\rangle$
\end_inset

 y 
\begin_inset Formula $\langle\cdot\rangle'$
\end_inset

, existe 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\in\mathbb{K}$
\end_inset

 tal que 
\begin_inset Formula $|B|=\lambda^{2}|A|$
\end_inset

.
 
\series bold
